dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents regional economic areas for Wisconsin in 2002. The dataset was originally published by the Federal Communications Commission in 2002.[The Regional Economic Areas also known as the Regional Economic Area Groupings for WCS which were created by Commission staff are an aggregation of MEAs into 12 regions.]
